    <title type="html"><![CDATA[[WordPress]Google +1 for WordPress]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.sammylin.tw/wordpressgoogle-1-for-wordpress/"/>
    <updated>2011-06-03T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.sammylin.tw/wordpressgoogle-1-for-wordpress</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><p>才在剛在用Google+1直接用WordPress模版加上Google +1的程式碼的過後沒多久想說來搜尋看看有沒有這個東西，果然是有的才在昨天2011/6/2發布第一版，功能是有的，不過有點簡陋跟<a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/facebook-comments-for-wordpress/" target="_blank">Facebook Comments for WordPress</a>比起來真的是遜色很多，但我們先來介紹一下，畢竟有潛力的一支程式！</p>  <table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="540">         <h4>The Google +1 plugin</h4>          <ul>           <li>下載位址：<a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/google/changelog/">http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/google/changelog/</a> </li>         </ul>       </td>     </tr>   </tbody></table>  <p>以下是他的設定：</p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image12.png"><img style="border-right-width: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb11.png" width="527" height="544" /></a>     <br /></p>  <ul>   <li>Appearance(設定大小) </li>    <li>Show +1s count(顯示+1數量) </li>    <li>Google +1 box position(放置位置) </li>    <li>Do NOT Google +1 box for thses post types(不顯示+1的文章類式) </li>    <li>Language(語言) </li>    <li>Show +1 on Front Page(顯示在首頁) </li> </ul>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image13.png"><img style="border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb12.png" width="544" height="149" /></a> </p>  <p>這放置的位置是在文章後面，不過蠻奇怪的位置，怎麼會是在標籤的前面，跟Facebook有點不同，希望他未來可以更完整啦！~~</p></p>

]]></content>
